Many a times we come across some social-networking sites icons and along with them, in a circle or something like that, a count, or a specific number is written, that function can be achieved by using badges.
Now again, this badges can be used inside the buttons or a tag also, and wherever you want.. ;-)


Now coming to labels
Labels are used to provide additional information about something:
Suppose we write some text in h1 and some other text in h3, now we want that Some information regarding both the texts must be shown in such a form that it attracts the attention.
This task is achieved by using the labels
Again, labes are availabe in info, success, waring, error, etc..
It is usually used along with some text.

